Table 1. Crystal data and structure refinement for 1

| Molecular formula | C14H14N2O9Zn2 |
|-------------------|--------------|
| Formula weight    | 485.01       |
| T (K)              | 293(2)       |
| λ (Å)              | 0.71073      |
| Crystal system    | monoclinic   |
| Space group       | P2(1)/n      |
| a (Å)              | 8.5819(17)   |
| b (Å)              | 11.478(2)    |
| c (Å)              | 15.558(3)    |
| β (°)              | 96.68(3)     |
| V (Å³)             | 1522.0(5)    |
| Z                  | 4            |
| μ (mm⁻¹)           | 3.212        |
| D calc (Mg/m³)     | 2.117        |
| F(000)             | 976          |
| Reflections collected | 6561     |
| Independent reflections (R int) | 3442(0.0463) |
| R1 (I>2σ(I))[^a]   | 0.0297       |
| wR2[^a]            | 0.0853       |

[^a]: R1=∑||F o|-|F c||/∑|F>0|; wR2=∑[w(F o²-F c²)²]/∑[w(F o²)²]¹/².
